BBEX3.M.BAM.USD.CA.AA.A01: Exchange rates for the US dollar in Bosnia and Hercegovina / USD 1 = BAM ... (buying)

General: On 11 August 1997, the convertible marka was introduced at the rate of BAD 100 = BAM 1. Initial exchange rates (buying/selling rate) to the US dollar on 1 October 1997: USD 1 = BAM 1.7555 / 1.7643.
Source: Centralna Banka Bosne i Hercegovine, Sarajevo.
